description:
Hi, my name is Eugene, and I am a professional developer with over 15 years’ experience in the tech/web development industry. During my time doing freelance work, I decided to continue my self-development and assembled a team. I’ve put together a group of highly talented developers which is called the Regulus Team. I wanted to surround myself with intelligent and bright personalities and create a unique brand that offers a better value to clients.

Previously, I have held a range of positions ranging from software engineer to CTO. Since then, I have progressed to building and working with large, highly-customized and integrated platforms, becoming an expert in Python, Apache and Nginx configuration, Unix, Typescript, Angular 2+, HTML, coding standards, infrastructure, performance auditing, back-of-house operations, single-page applications, version control, and much more.

I absolutely adore writing code and in spite of my vast experience, I spend a lot of time every day learning new languages, frameworks, workflow optimizations, etc. I am trying to code in the best possible manner following the best established world practices.

I am able to jump into a new project quickly and creatively solve problems. When it comes to debugging, I have a great eye for spotting bugs. I try to predict all possible complications before a project begins. During my 13 years of experience in all sorts of codebases, I’m able to start and complete work quicker than experienced contractors. Your time is valuable, so I won’t waste it. I am online and available to my clients 24/7 by phone for urgent issues.

My mission is to bring you excellent project satisfaction by providing quality and professional work.

The list of technologies I frequently use and the level of my experience:
-         Python (Django, Django Rest Framework, Numpy, Scipy, Sklearn, Wagtail, Reportlab): Senior Level;
-         Apache and Nginx configuration: Mid-Level;
-         Unix (prefer Debian-based systems): Mid-Level;
-         JavaScript: Senior Level;
-         Typescript: Senior Level;
-         Angular 2+: Senior Level;
-         Jquery: Mid-Level;
-         HTML/CSS/SCSS: Senior Level;

Hello, everyone!
I'm a full-stack/devops engineer with over five years of professional experience.
I have experience building and deploying scalable and performant web applications, Restful APIs, microservices and more.

My Skills:
— Python, Django, Flask, FastAPI, Selenium, Celery;
— Databases: Postgresql, Mysql, MongoDB, Elasticsearch, Redis;
— Front End: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, AJAX, HTMX;
— Infrastructure: AWS, GCP, Digital Ocean;
— VCS: Git - GitHub & Git Actions, Gitlab;
— Automated Provisionning/Deployment: AWS CDK, Terraform, Ansible, Pulumni.
— Continuous Integration/Deployment setup and maintenance: Git Actions, Jenkins, Code Pipeline, Cloud Build.
— Containerization and Orchestration: Docker, Podman, Kubernetes, GKE, EKS.

Looking forward to working with you.
